<script setup>
import GeoTiffTest from './components/GeoTiffTest.vue';
</script>

<style lang="scss">
html, body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  height: 100%;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}

#app {
  height: 100%;
}

// Element Plus 暗色主题覆盖
:root {
  --el-color-primary: #1890ff;
  --el-color-success: #52c41a;
  --el-color-warning: #faad14;
  --el-color-danger: #ff4d4f;
  --el-color-info: #909399;
}

.el-button {
  &--primary {
    --el-button-bg-color: var(--el-color-primary);
    --el-button-border-color: var(--el-color-primary);
    --el-button-hover-bg-color: var(--el-color-primary-light-3);
    --el-button-hover-border-color: var(--el-color-primary-light-3);
  }

  &--success {
    --el-button-bg-color: var(--el-color-success);
    --el-button-border-color: var(--el-color-success);
    --el-button-hover-bg-color: var(--el-color-success-light-3);
    --el-button-hover-border-color: var(--el-color-success-light-3);
  }
}

.el-input {
  --el-input-bg-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  --el-input-border-color: transparent;
  --el-input-hover-border-color: var(--el-color-primary);
  --el-input-focus-border-color: var(--el-color-primary);
  --el-input-text-color: #fff;
  --el-input-placeholder-color: #8c8c8c;
}

.el-select {
  --el-select-input-focus-border-color: var(--el-color-primary);
  --el-select-border-color-hover: var(--el-color-primary);
}

.el-pagination {
  --el-pagination-bg-color: transparent;
  --el-pagination-hover-color: var(--el-color-primary);
  --el-pagination-button-bg-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  --el-pagination-button-color: #fff;
  --el-pagination-button-disabled-bg-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  --el-pagination-button-disabled-color: #8c8c8c;
}

.el-table {
  --el-table-border-color: #303030;
  --el-table-header-bg-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  --el-table-header-text-color: #fff;
  --el-table-text-color: #fff;
  --el-table-row-hover-bg-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
}

.el-dialog {
  --el-dialog-bg-color: #001529;
  --el-dialog-title-color: #fff;
  --el-dialog-content-color: #bfbfbf;
}

.el-message {
  --el-message-bg-color: #001529;
  --el-message-text-color: #fff;
  --el-message-border-color: #303030;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  border-radius: 3px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 3px;

  &:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }
}
</style>
